attributes.Long form description: The student is assembling a rolling cart. They start by screwing the side bars together, then the base frame. The base frame is screwed onto the side bars. The student assembles the bottom tray and screws it onto the brackets. The student assembles the two remaining trays and screws the top tray and middle tray onto the brackets. The student assembles the bottom wheels.

attributes.Transcription: Hello. Thank you for agreeing to take part in our study.
